{"tid":771766,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"前人力甄燊港：港人應用大慈悲的心去接受解放軍穿軍服外出，讓大家能互相了解～","createTime":"2018-08-08T08:42:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-08T09:47:35.000Z","uid":49388,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"416261bec4258107328b706da43436afcf1b64ef","tid":771766,"uid":49388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T08:42:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/QvrciUyULXg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FQvrciUyULXg&d=OSYCL8qBPEKgVfYrwvjrwoM9LuuOiGKVuJxWWRW4JEQ%3D&h=6bed4a71\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/QvrciUyULXg</a><br />\n<br />\n1.解放軍平時已經少機會出外離開軍營，就算出外都只係鴨仔團形式。<br />\n<br />\n2.佢地為能夠駐守香港是感到十分光榮，經歷兩年駐守回到家鄉後亦會為此感到嬌傲，可惜因在駐港時出外機會較少令人感到十分可惜。<br />\n<br />\n3.駐港解放軍不是㓋水猛獸，經過這廿年的駐港部隊沒有做過咩壞事。<br />\n<br />\n4.問心講，一隊軍隊駐守年俾佢出去行下並不是問題。<br />\n<br />\n5.俾得佢外出穿軍服做壞事反而冇咁方便做壞事。<br />\n<br />\n6.這次是一個非常難得既機會讓解放軍了解香港人是非常友善，大家應放下極端而且扭曲的敵對心態，要用大慈悲的心去感化別人，否則俾人打到仆街唔好怨。<br />\n<br />\n7.出外軍服應講究，並不應持有武器外出，以免被人混淆有維持治安的職責。"},{"pid":"a12dd5ad6827fe8bc42bd4590b62b49a3044c240","tid":771766,"uid":50740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T08:44:58.000Z","msg":"著晒便服方便偷拍同捉人上洗頭艇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1cf1130cd73f1ca98baa89de9a8ac7f1f77a574","tid":771766,"uid":49388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a12dd5ad6827fe8bc42bd4590b62b49a3044c240","tid":771766,"uid":50740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T08:44:58.000Z","msg":"著晒便服方便偷拍同捉人上洗頭艇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T08:45:59.000Z","msg":"甄生真係明智<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec78c9bdcc4a2e0b738c9e000d5c822f1ecad9d8","tid":771766,"uid":49388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T08:49:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c97514b91138986e